set autoindent

" Commands
nmap ; :

" New lines
nnoremap <Enter> o<Esc>
nnoremap <S-Enter> O<Esc>

" Indent and append
nnoremap cc ddO

" Yanking and pasting
vnoremap <space>y "*y
nnoremap <space>p "*p
nnoremap <space>P "*P

" Saving
nnoremap <space><esc> :w<CR>

" Split navigation
map <Space> <Nop>
nnoremap <C-h> <C-W><C-H>
nnoremap <C-j> <C-W><C-J>
nnoremap <C-k> <C-W><C-K>
nnoremap <C-l> <C-W><C-L>